						<b>Tong-baechu-Kimchi (unsliced Chinese cabbage Kimchi)</b><br><br>
						Cabbage is salted down and thin strips of radish are mixed with powdered red pepper, green onions, garlic, and salt-fermented seafoods. The mixture is inserted between cabbage leaves. Kimchi thus made is put in the earthenware pot and fermented. This is the basic of Korean Kimchi. </td>
