					<tr valign="top">
						<td width="10" class="o">*</td>
						<td class="o">Chinese cabbage is rich in vitamin C and minerals such as calcium and potassium. When too much sodium is absorbed, it balances and is good for preventing atherosclerosis.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="20" border="0"></td></tr>
